queries.sql: SELECT hocsinh.*, taikhoan.*, lop.TenLop FROM hocsinh JOIN taikhoan ON taikhoan.MaTK = hocsinh.MaTK JOIN hocsinh_lop ON hocsinh.MaHS = hocsinh_lop.MaHS JOIN lop ON lop.MaLop = hocsinh_lop.MaLop WHERE hocsinh_lop.MaLop = '1' AND hocsinh_lop.NamHoc = '2023-2024'
